{"tid":1856810,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"禍不單行！湖北爆肺炎 湖南就爆H5N1禽流感：4500隻雞發病亡","createTime":"2020-02-01T21:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T02:28:22.000Z","uid":152123,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"40053299000aff93597ae788716ea78aa9170b2e","tid":1856810,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T21:10:22.000Z","msg":"湖南邵陽市H5N1禽流感　4500隻雞發病亡<br />\n<br />\n農業農村部公布，湖南省邵陽市發生H5N1亞型高致病性禽流感疫情。根據公布，雙清區一個養殖戶飼養7850隻雞，其中4500隻發病死亡。當地已撲殺17828隻家禽，全部病死和撲殺家禽均已無害化處理。<br />\n<br />\nRTHK 2020-02-02 04:42:50"},{"pid":"3c9959d964c19710ff4a97f6b3ea7dd7bc53217b","tid":1856810,"uid":152123,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T21:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://news.cctv.com/20080523/images/1211517835274_1211517835274_r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cctv.com%2F20080523%2Fimages%2F1211517835274_1211517835274_r.jpg&h=7a2f7ed8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80d72d30f6ff53510acf1492ad95344b5c2afa04","tid":1856810,"uid":206617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T21:13:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb785da511439d514e670209479db639b5ed0a7","tid":1856810,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80d72d30f6ff53510acf1492ad95344b5c2afa04","tid":1856810,"uid":206617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T21:13:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T21:20:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hk